	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I have made a simple animated spritefield using a bit of code from a friend of mine (nocarrier who used to post here) and a bit of nerdy nights code and a little bit of code I wrote myself. It has 4 different animated sprites to switch between and 4 palettes to cycle though.<br /><br />I know it isn't spectacular or anything but I am quite proud of it! <br /><br /><img src="http://i.imgur.com/NT64Rfn.png?1" alt="Image" /><br /><br />D pad - sprite direction<br />Select - change palette<br />start - stop sprite movement<br />B - change sprites

		
